      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This unit has been preserved with exacting standards, showing no signs of wear and boasting a flawless aesthetic both internally and externally. It represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of collector-grade quality. Precise mechanical integrity and an immaculate cabin ensure an unparalleled driving experience for the most fastidious professional.",
